com.lucidworks.fusion.connector.plugin.api.plugin

Class ConnectorPlugin.Builder

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.lucidworks.fusion.connector.plugin.api.plugin.ConnectorPlugin.Builder
  • Enclosing class:
    ConnectorPlugin

    public static class ConnectorPlugin.Builder
extends java.lang.Object
    A simple Builder for a ConnectorPlugin. Note that while the withFetcher(Class, Module...) can be omitted, it is expected that all Connectors MUST register a Fetcher component.
